# Build-time public env (Astro). No variables are currently required.

# Admin auth secrets are NOT build-time env — they are Worker secrets.
# In production set them with `wrangler secret put`:
#   SESSION_SECRET   32+ random bytes; signs the admin session cookie (rotate to log out everywhere)
#   SETUP_TOKEN      bootstrap token for the first passkey; delete after setup
#
# For local `wrangler`/preview runs, put them in a gitignored `.dev.vars` file:
#   SESSION_SECRET="..."
#   SETUP_TOKEN="..."
